ther, the 2D density, magnetic field and Alfv\\'en speed maps described\nhere give a more accurate method for determining the fundamental properties of\nshocks and their relation to CMEs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Feb 2014 16:35:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Mar 2014 14:38:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-05-08"}
