ial behavior of DNP dynamics and the subsequent relaxation is\nmediated by the nuclei of $^{29}$Si surrounding $^{31}$P donors, which affect\nthe transition probabilities of the forbidden cross-relaxation processes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Feb 2014 10:57:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 12 Mar 2014 12:57:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 2 May 2014 10:49:33 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 5 May 2014 08:57:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-03"}
